{"tid":1630874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無差別攻擊路人割唔割?","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:39.000Z","uid":84267,"like":27,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"45183f2afc0d32fe9fbb252283b172fc1070a43f","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"成日話核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n如果無差別攻擊路人割唔割?<br />\n打爛珠寶店偷嘢搶嘢割唔割?<br />\n火燒所有店舖不理黃藍割唔割?<br />\n斬埋你老母割唔割?<br />\n做埋真暴徒割唔割?<br />\n<br />\n你話, &quot;前線唔係冇腦&quot;, 一定唔會咁做<br />\n我夠知啦屌<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有鬼</span>做上述嘅野, 然後有人<span style=\"color: red;\">開post認頭</span>呢?<br />\n然後話:<br />\n&quot;死咗好多人命啦你仲咁潔癖&quot;<br />\n&quot;核爆都唔割&quot; &quot;兄弟爬山&quot;  &quot;不分化不割蓆&quot; <br />\n&quot;你批判就係步雨革後塵&quot; &quot;收皮啦捉鬼撚&quot;<br />\n&quot;你有咩資格出聲? 冷氣軍事&quot;  &quot;相信前線&quot;  <br />\n&quot;2019仲講底線&quot; <br />\n<br />\n對方偽激進一直利用我地核爆都唔割, 逼我哋認頭所有野<br />\n<br />\n所以每次有人/鬼做衰嘢, D人嘅留言一定係<span style=\"color: orange;\"> &quot;唔割, 不過唔建議咁咁咁..&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<strong>表明原則底線</strong>極之重要. 原則, 貌似係限制自己. 但其實更加係<strong>保護我哋嘅運動</strong>免被抹黑. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呢個時刻, 不停標榜無底線無原則嘅, 一定係鬼.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言, 裝修四大分類一定要繼續推, 唔可以沉<br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614174</a><br />\n四大分類：黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯，OK嘛？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU</a>"},{"pid":"b2ce0c55fe1808f5cd264f1c595d245cf3109254","tid":1630874,"uid":73419,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e1f304bcad74f2eee16f399a75b8405d7e4814","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2ce0c55fe1808f5cd264f1c595d245cf3109254","tid":1630874,"uid":73419,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n睇文先啦屌你"},{"pid":"8339929d2b1b7a20fb39794641cd44ef01729e15","tid":1630874,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"打路人？屌你老母你唔去打你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ede4b6c8feec77a830f3150e14bcd63e12e3f5","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8339929d2b1b7a20fb39794641cd44ef01729e15","tid":1630874,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"打路人？屌你老母你唔去打你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"睇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a738cfbf841d0009265feb70c8ff92ac16a9aaf4","tid":1630874,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2ce0c55fe1808f5cd264f1c595d245cf3109254","tid":1630874,"uid":73419,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"[重新推出]三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630313</a>"},{"pid":"bec4bc620949861cbdd51497218dd3fe7c9e9485","tid":1630874,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e1f304bcad74f2eee16f399a75b8405d7e4814","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2ce0c55fe1808f5cd264f1c595d245cf3109254","tid":1630874,"uid":73419,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n睇文先啦屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"[重新推出]三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630313</a>"},{"pid":"fef6e22ae60acc8cf4b1cae99a5067126cb19c27","tid":1630874,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45183f2afc0d32fe9fbb252283b172fc1070a43f","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"成日話核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n如果無差別攻擊路人割唔割?<br />\n打爛珠寶店偷嘢搶嘢割唔割?<br />\n火燒所有店舖不理黃藍割唔割?<br />\n斬埋你老母割唔割?<br />\n做埋真暴徒割唔割?<br />\n<br />\n你話, &quot;前線唔係冇腦&quot;, 一定唔會咁做<br />\n我夠知啦屌<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有鬼</span>做上述嘅野, 然後有人<span style=\"color: red;\">開post認頭</span>呢?<br />\n然後話:<br />\n&quot;死咗好多人命啦你仲咁潔癖&quot;<br />\n&quot;核爆都唔割&quot; &quot;兄弟爬山&quot;  &quot;不分化不割蓆&quot; <br />\n&quot;你批判就係步雨革後塵&quot; &quot;收皮啦捉鬼撚&quot;<br />\n&quot;你有咩資格出聲? 冷氣軍事&quot;  &quot;相信前線&quot;  <br />\n&quot;2019仲講底線&quot; <br />\n<br />\n對方偽激進一直利用我地核爆都唔割, 逼我哋認頭所有野<br />\n<br />\n所以每次有人/鬼做衰嘢, D人嘅留言一定係<span style=\"color: orange;\"> &quot;唔割, 不過唔建議咁咁咁..&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<strong>表明原則底線</strong>極之重要. 原則, 貌似係限制自己. 但其實更加係<strong>保護我哋嘅運動</strong>免被抹黑. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呢個時刻, 不停標榜無底線無原則嘅, 一定係鬼.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言, 裝修四大分類一定要繼續推, 唔可以沉<br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614174</a><br />\n四大分類：黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯，OK嘛？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"如果我唔係P牌<br />\n我一定負皮你"},{"pid":"b68d78c61b9023d3a61984f37be6dfba4ab1f4e7","tid":1630874,"uid":284304,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"根本連登最近就一路鼓吹激進<br />\n特別係緊急法呢幾日<br />\n大量post都話要裝修呢間個間 <br />\n然後又有大量打手出黎話&quot;革命阿&quot;,&quot;核彈都唔割?&quot;等等既道德勒索<br />\n根本上有幾多破壞係黑警做既都冇人知<br />\n連登就攬唔切上身咁"},{"pid":"0a5ad31fab309b9f9f97e714de4d9ed38df7ab52","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bec4bc620949861cbdd51497218dd3fe7c9e9485","tid":1630874,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e1f304bcad74f2eee16f399a75b8405d7e4814","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2ce0c55fe1808f5cd264f1c595d245cf3109254","tid":1630874,"uid":73419,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n睇文先啦屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"[重新推出]三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630313</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n<br />\n防止分化方法就係一套公認嘅原則"},{"pid":"8fb5ca427dc369779116ac644296884fc4f7e2da","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef6e22ae60acc8cf4b1cae99a5067126cb19c27","tid":1630874,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45183f2afc0d32fe9fbb252283b172fc1070a43f","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"成日話核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n如果無差別攻擊路人割唔割?<br />\n打爛珠寶店偷嘢搶嘢割唔割?<br />\n火燒所有店舖不理黃藍割唔割?<br />\n斬埋你老母割唔割?<br />\n做埋真暴徒割唔割?<br />\n<br />\n你話, &quot;前線唔係冇腦&quot;, 一定唔會咁做<br />\n我夠知啦屌<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有鬼</span>做上述嘅野, 然後有人<span style=\"color: red;\">開post認頭</span>呢?<br />\n然後話:<br />\n&quot;死咗好多人命啦你仲咁潔癖&quot;<br />\n&quot;核爆都唔割&quot; &quot;兄弟爬山&quot;  &quot;不分化不割蓆&quot; <br />\n&quot;你批判就係步雨革後塵&quot; &quot;收皮啦捉鬼撚&quot;<br />\n&quot;你有咩資格出聲? 冷氣軍事&quot;  &quot;相信前線&quot;  <br />\n&quot;2019仲講底線&quot; <br />\n<br />\n對方偽激進一直利用我地核爆都唔割, 逼我哋認頭所有野<br />\n<br />\n所以每次有人/鬼做衰嘢, D人嘅留言一定係<span style=\"color: orange;\"> &quot;唔割, 不過唔建議咁咁咁..&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<strong>表明原則底線</strong>極之重要. 原則, 貌似係限制自己. 但其實更加係<strong>保護我哋嘅運動</strong>免被抹黑. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呢個時刻, 不停標榜無底線無原則嘅, 一定係鬼.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言, 裝修四大分類一定要繼續推, 唔可以沉<br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614174</a><br />\n四大分類：黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯，OK嘛？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajhBbpU</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"如果我唔係P牌<br />\n我一定負皮你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"負皮我乜? 有講錯?"},{"pid":"98516cc0ff794c609e7f041e1b400c1c6b3f2493","tid":1630874,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68d78c61b9023d3a61984f37be6dfba4ab1f4e7","tid":1630874,"uid":284304,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"根本連登最近就一路鼓吹激進<br />\n特別係緊急法呢幾日<br />\n大量post都話要裝修呢間個間 <br />\n然後又有大量打手出黎話&quot;革命阿&quot;,&quot;核彈都唔割?&quot;等等既道德勒索<br />\n根本上有幾多破壞係黑警做既都冇人知<br />\n連登就攬唔切上身咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"所以原則好緊要"},{"pid":"669e669d69a146902a03b982100273d9cdd1af66","tid":1630874,"uid":311701,"like":0,